<body id="background-color">

  <h1>READ. <span id="emphasis">LOCAL.</span> NEWS.</h1>

  <p class="summary"> A <em id="cross"> Cross-Comparitive </em> Tool: Each country's RSS feeds are sourced <span id="underline">for you.</span> </p>

<style>
  .earth{
    position:absolute;
    top:320px;
    left:0;
    right:0;
    margin:auto;
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background-image:url(https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UUXaK5GCj-k/UcsKJRMgkVI/AAAAAAAACfM/sePP_H08JTQ/s1600/1.jpg);
    border-radius:50%;
    background-size:cover;
    box-shadow:-20px -20px 50px 2px #000 inset, 0 0 20px 2px #000;
    animation: spin 30s linear alternate infinite;
    -webkit-transform:rotate
  }

  @keyframes spin{
    100%{background-position:100%;}
  }



</style>

<div class="earth"> </div>

